                <h1>Understanding the Main Character in "The Yellow Wallpaper"</h1>
                <p>The main character of "The Yellow Wallpaper" is a woman suffering from postpartum depression, confined to a room by her husband for the sake of her mental health. As she becomes obsessed with the wallpaper, it reflects her descent into madness and her struggle against the oppressive constraints of her marriage and society.</p>
